'''馬龍尼禮天主教布宜諾斯艾利斯聖沙爾貝勒教區'''（{{lang-la|Eparchia Sancti Sarbelii Bonaërensis Maronitarum}}、{{lang-es|Eparquía San Charbel en Buenos Aires de los maronitas}}）是[[東儀天主教|東儀天主教]]以[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]首都[[布宜諾斯艾利斯|布宜諾斯艾利斯]]為中心的一個[[教區|教區]]（[[馬龍尼禮教會|馬龍尼禮教會]]），屬[[天主教布宜諾斯艾利斯總教區|布宜諾斯艾利斯總教區]]。

教區成立於1990年10月5日，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.misionlibanesa.com.ar/obispado-argentina2.htm |title=Obispado Maronita en la Argentina  |access-date=2013-04-11 |archive-date=2021-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426043827/http://www.misionlibanesa.com.ar/obispado-argentina2.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>2009年有教友700,000人。教區下轄四個堂區，有卅二名司鐸。現任教區主教為{{link-en|赫比卜·沙米埃|Habib Chamieh|若望·赫比卜·沙米埃}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 22.11.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/22/0912/01905.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-11-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191123051641/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/22/0912/01905.html |archivedate=2019-11-23 |language=it |date=2019-11-22}}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-en|沙爾貝勒·喬治·邁爾希|Charbel Georges Merhi}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 17.04.2013 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/04/17/0233/00528.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-11-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191123053812/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/04/17/0233/00528.html |archivedate=2019-11-23 |language=it |date=2013-04-17}}</ref>。

